cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with image inpainting, which is a computer vision task, and proposes an end-to-end network for the same. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses deep generative models and addresses the challenge of synthesizing new content in inconsistent regions, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves image processing and manipulation, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
